pageProduct.name: OsteVit-D Vitamin D3 Liquid 50ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

OsteVit-D Vitamin D3 Liquid enhances calcium absorption to maintain strong bones. It contains 250 doses of Vitamin D3 1000IU per bottle.

OsteVit-D Vitamin D3 Liquid suits adults and children 12 years of age and over, tose at risk of low vitamin D levels and those with difficulty swallowing tablets.

The pleasant tasting caramel flavoured liquid is colour and sugar free.

Size: 50ml

KEY FEATURES

• • Enhances Calcium absorbtion
• • Maintains bone density and strength
• • Supports bone health and muscle function
• • Maintains healthy immune system function
• • Suitable for vegetarians
• • Free From Sugar, Gluten, Yeast, Starch, Wheat, Soy, Lactose, Shellfish, Egg, Artificial, colours, Gelatin

Warnings

"Vitamins can only be of assistance if dietary vitamin intake is inadequate.
Contains sodium benzoate"

Ingredients

butylated hydroxytoluene, citric acid, dibasic sodium phosphate heptahydrate, dl-alpha-tocopherol, Flavour, glycerol, polysorbate 80, purified water, sodium benzoate, sucralose, vegetable oil

Active Ingredients: Contains Vitamin D3 1000IU (cholecalciferol 25 micrograms) per tablet

Directions

Adults and children over 12 years of age: One tablet daily or as directed by your healthcare professional. Tablets may be crushed if required. For children under 12 years of age OsteVit-D Children's Oral Drops are recommended.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C
